<body>
<div id="header" class="head head-nobg">
    <div class="top">
        <div class="topnav">
            <a href="{php echo create_url('index');}" target="_blank">微易首页</a>|
            <a href="{php echo create_url('member/login');}" target="_blank">登录</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="container">
    <form id="myform"  class="form-horizontal form-box" action="" method="post">
        <div class="form-header">
            <span class="pull-left">轻松绑定公众账号，只需三步！</span>
        </div>

        <div class="stepbar stepbar-separate stepbar-three">
            <div class="stepbar-inner">
                <div class="stepbar-item first ">
                    <span class="stepbar-number"><em>1</em></span>
                    <span class="stepbar-desc">填写您的公共账号信息</span>
                    <hr class="stepbar-progrees">
                </div>
                <div class="stepbar-item ">
                    <span class="stepbar-number"><em>2</em></span>
                    <span class="stepbar-desc">请将此URL及Token填到微信公众平台</span>
                    <hr class="stepbar-progrees">
                </div>
                <div class="stepbar-item last active">
                    <span class="stepbar-number"><em>3</em></span>
                    <span class="stepbar-desc">设置用户欢迎信息及默认回复语</span>
                    <hr class="stepbar-progrees">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-body">
            <div class="control-group">
                <label class="control-label" for="welcome">用户欢迎语：</label>
                <div class="controls">
                    <div class="textarea-face">
                        <textarea name="welcome" id="welcome" ></textarea><a inputid="welcome" href="javascript:;" class="iconEmotion"><i class="icon icon-face"></i>添加表情</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="control-group">
                <label class="control-label" for="default">默认回复语：</label>
                <div class="controls">
                    <div class="textarea-face">
                        <textarea name="default" id="default"></textarea><a inputid="default" href="javascript:;" class="iconEmotion"><i class="icon icon-face"></i>添加表情</a>


                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <input type="hidden" name="token" value="{$_W['token']}">
            <input type="hidden" name="weid" value="{$id}">
            <input type="hidden" name="step" value="3">
            <div class="control-group">
                <div class="controls">
                    <button name="submit" class="hide" value="1"></button>
                    <a type="button" class="btn btn-submit" href="{$pre_url}">上一步</a>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-submit"    href="#myModal" data-toggle="modal" >下一步</button>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </form>
    
    <a class="scrollup" href="javascript:;" title="TOP">TOP</a>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="./resource/script/jquery.scrollUp.min.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript">
        $('.scrollup').scrollUp();
    </script>
</div>

<div class="modal hide fade modal-message" id="myModal">
    <div class="modal-header">
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">&times;</button>
        <h3>完成绑定，测验一下</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-body">
        <p>用微信个人号关注您的公众号，收到您设置的用户欢迎语，说明您已经成功绑定！</p>
        <p>若您已关注公共账号，用微信个人号给你的公众号发送"T"，收到“<em class="text-error">诚心成易</em>”，说明您已经成功绑定！</p>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-footer">
        <a href="javascript:;" data-dismiss="modal" class="btn btn-cancle">重新绑定</a>
        <a id="successblind"  href="javascript:;" class="btn btn-submit">成功绑定</a>
    </div>
</div>
